.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Helper class that manages an interrupt flag, and allows a thread or signal to interrupt another thread\&.

.PP
This class is safe to be used in a signal handler\&. If sending an interrupt from a signal handler is not necessary, the more lightweight \fBCThreadInterrupt\fP class can be used instead\&. 
